            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>愿先知（愿主福安之）的叔父，艾卜•莱海卜•本•阿卜杜勒•穆台列卜的双手因他自己的恶行而受伤！当时他迫害先知（愿主福安之）而未得逞。</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "111:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>无论是他的钱财还是子嗣都无济于他，都不能替他阻挡惩罚，也不能为他唤来怜悯。</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "111:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>复活日他将进入那有着火焰的火狱，</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "111:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他那曾在路上抛掷棘刺伤害先知（愿主福安之）的妻子乌姆·杰米莱也将进入火狱。</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "111:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>她的脖子上系有一条拽她到火狱的致命的绳子。</p>"
        }
    }
}